name: Arms Dealer
description:
6025-
Public markets are highly regulated, only open for a select amount of time and only available to the social elite. Black markets and secondary markets thrive out of sight. Avoiding the gaze of the colonial church system.

These hidden markets sell assortments of regulated plants and biological material from unnamed sources and practices. This is not the place to strike up a deal.
